Barry Watson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barry_Watson_(actor) 0 Michael Barrett "Barry" Watson (born April 23, 1974) is an American actor, known for his roles of Matthew "Matt" Camden on 7th Heaven, Brian Davis in What About Brian and Todd Deepler in Samantha Who?.
